    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove PCV 50km radius rule for Drivers under the age of 20",
        "additional_details": "We believe this restriction is creating an unnecessary barrier to coach industry recruitment. So many talented young drivers coming from school cannot gain a career due to this restriction.\r\n \r\nRef: https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1116842/inf52-large-vehicles-you-can-drive-using-your-car-or-lorry-licence.pdf\r\n",
        "background": "Currently PCV drivers who are 18 and 19 cannot drive a minibus/bus/coach on a route longer than 50km. We want the Government to remove this restriction.",
